title: A Killer Within [DVDRIP][2004][English Subs Esp]
description: Addison Terrill (Howell), a Dallas attorney, comes home one night to find his wife brutally murdered with the words &quot;We're even now&quot; scrawled across the bedroom wall. The cops suspect he killed her, and now Addison must race through the underside of Dallas to find the only other suspect. His ally is a grudging ex-cop (Esposito) who knows what it takes to deliver justice. If they can overcome their differences, they'll be able to solve the case before anyone else gets hurt.
